                    Test 05 History file
                    --------------------
This file should be used by the test developer to briefly
summarize all major modifications introduced in the code and keep
track of all tags.

     ----------------------------------------------------------
     * Reverse chronological order (last date on top), please *
     ----------------------------------------------------------

May 28, 2003  Gabriele Cosmo (test05-V05-01-00)
- Added flag G4USE_STEP in GNUmakefile.
- Limit usage to Linux-egcs and non-ISO/ANSI compilers.

Mar 12, 2003  John Allison (test05-V05-00-00)
- Added HepRep to vis manager.

29th Nov 2001  Gabriele Cosmo (test05-V03-02-00)
- fixed ISO compilation inconsistencies on GNUmakefile.

18th Oct 2001  Steve O'Neale
- update reference outputs in tests directory

15th Feb 2001 Steve O'Neale (test05-V03-00-00)
- Update large_N test output

25th November 2000 Steve O'Neale (tagset210)
- Update test outputs for min.delta energy cut

June 17, 2000  John Allison  (test05-V01-01-01)
- Updated test05.out for geant4-01-01-ref-06.

17 Apr., 1999 H.Kurashige 
- Modify SetCuts() and ConstructParticle() in Tst05PhysicsList
- Modify BeginOfRunAction() and EndOfRunAction() in Tst05RunAction

9th August 1998  John Allison
- Changed G4UIterminal to G4UIGAG.

June 27, 98 G. Cosmo
- Created.

